<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hardship-n">hardship <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hɑːdʃɪp/    美 /'hɑːrdʃɪp/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>苦难；困苦；苦事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Hardship is the first access to truth. 
苦难是通往真理的第一条路。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Not until he went through real hardship did he realize the love we have for our families is important. 
直到经历了真正的苦难，他才意识到我们对家人的爱很重要。</p><footer>2013 福建</footer></div></div>